From 0000000000000000000000000000000000000000 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: David Nystrom <david.nystrom@est.tech>
Date: Sun, 11 May 2026 20:00:00 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] python: rename benchmark_app entry point to benchmark_app_python3

Avoid a file collision with the C++ benchmark_app sample binary at
/usr/bin/benchmark_app when both samples and python3 are enabled.

Upstream-Status: Inappropriate [OE-specific]

Signed-off-by: David Nystrom <david.nystrom@est.tech>
---
 setup.py | 2 +-
 1 file changed, 1 insertion(+), 1 deletion(-)

diff --git a/setup.py b/setup.py
--- a/setup.py
+++ b/setup.py
@@ -234,7 +234,7 @@
     "benchmark_app": {
         "entry_point": {
             "console_scripts": [
-                "benchmark_app = openvino.tools.benchmark.main:main",
+                "benchmark_app_python3 = openvino.tools.benchmark.main:main",
             ],
         },
         "name": "benchmark_app",
